"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-29-biles-stuns-olympic-return-nadal-sets-djokovic-clash\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP) - Simone Biles dazzled a star-studded crowd as she returned to the Olympic stage on Sunday, while Rafael Nadal set up a showdown with career-long rival Novak Djokovic.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 187, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.7783821371324114, \"rank\": 0.28470942422091805, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 118, \"end\": 130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 172, \"end\": 186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles's return was one of the highlights of day two as the sun returned to Paris, with 13 gold medals up for grabs, including a blockbuster swimming duel.\", \"from\": 189, \"to\": 343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 264, \"end\": 269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.038722793252858e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hollywood star Tom Cruise and pop stars Lady Gaga and Ariana Grande were among a host of A-listers crowded into a packed Bercy Arena as United States superstar Biles began her quest for Olympic gymnastics redemption.\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 345, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.726624618104598e-14, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 360, \"end\": 370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}, {\"begin\": 385, \"end\": 394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}, {\"begin\": 399, \"end\": 412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariana Grande\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\"}, {\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bercy Arena\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\"}, {\"begin\": 481, \"end\": 494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.999897156906629, \"rank\": 0.00010285347897268721, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old four-time Olympic champion, widely regarded as the greatest gymnast in history, entered the arena to a standing ovation and a deafening roar greeted her introduction.\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 745, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The American star acknowledged the support with a wave and she blew a kiss to the crowd after her image was flashed up on a giant scoreboard.\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 888, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 751, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Standardbred\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.2869017825610622e-12, \"text\": \"American star\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Standardbred\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Standardbred\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles opened her qualifying with a sublime performance on the beam, finishing second behind China's Zhou Yaqin.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 982, \"end\": 987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.5452553651796057, \"rank\": 0.8047935575264906, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 990, \"end\": 994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhou_dynasty\", \"score\": 0.9648316167043545, \"rank\": 0.021061324806489527, \"text\": \"Zhou\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhou_dynasty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhou_dynasty\"}, {\"begin\": 995, \"end\": 1000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yaqeen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yaqin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yaqeen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yaqeen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She tweaked her left calf warming up for her second apparatus, the floor exercise, but still topped the standings.\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1117, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She also led the vault and was still clinging to the eighth and last finals berth in uneven bars with two qualifying sessions to come.\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles topped the all-around standings with 59.566 points, while the United States led the way in the team competition.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1323, \"end\": 1336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.999897156906629, \"rank\": 0.00010285347897268721, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's incredible,\\\" said US team technical lead Chellsie Memmel.\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1399, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999713509, \"rank\": 2.8539769829806748e-11, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1422, \"end\": 1437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chellsie_Memmel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chellsie Memmel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chellsie_Memmel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chellsie_Memmel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What she was able to do looking like she has soreness or something in her leg is remarkable.\\\"\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-time world champion is competing in Paris three years after her campaign at the Tokyo Olympics unravelled due to a disorientating condition gymnasts call \\\"twisties\\\".\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1578, \"end\": 1583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.038722793252858e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She still went home with a silver and bronze and was lauded for speaking openly about her mental health struggles.\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1823, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At Roland Garros, Nadal shrugged off lingering injury concerns to beat 83rd-ranked Hungarian Marton Fucsovics 6-1, 4-6, 6-4 despite sporting strapping on his injured right thigh and will play top seed Djokovic next.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 2040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1843, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.80840268537058e-12, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 2026, \"end\": 2034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.11459627767468e-12, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His meeting with the Serbian 24-time major winner will be the 60th of their storied careers.\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2063, \"end\": 2070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.9833578382910245, \"rank\": 0.016836381563988954, \"text\": \"Serbian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of course, it's beautiful to play against one of the two biggest rivals that I had in my career, especially on this court,\\\" said the 38-year-old Nadal.\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2282, \"end\": 2287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.80840268537058e-12, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But situations are completely different for him, for me.\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2347, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's being very competitive.\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was not being very competitive for the last two years, so in that case, I think probably he is the clear favourite.\\\"\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2495, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the basketball court, Kevin Durant returned from injury to produce a shooting masterclass as the United States launched the defence of their Olympic crown with a 110-84 win over Serbia.\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2528, \"end\": 2534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"score\": 0.9999997852528626, \"rank\": 2.1474715785398624e-07, \"text\": \"Durant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\"}, {\"begin\": 2597, \"end\": 2610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.999897156906629, \"rank\": 0.00010285347897268721, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2678, \"end\": 2684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9104263979089582, \"rank\": 0.09838636931520155, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Durant shot a near-perfect 8-of-9 from the field to finish with 23 points in a convincing win for the reigning champions, who are eyeing a fifth-straight Olympic crown.\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All eyes will be on the battle for gold in the swimming pool at La Defense Arena on Sunday evening, where Britain's Adam Peaty faces a duel with China's world champion Qin Haiyang in the 100m breaststroke.\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 3062, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2963, \"end\": 2970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.999910230340013, \"rank\": 8.977771035819869e-05, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 2973, \"end\": 2983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}, {\"begin\": 3002, \"end\": 3007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.5452553651796057, \"rank\": 0.8047935575264906, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 3025, \"end\": 3036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Haiyang\", \"score\": 0.9999938624998401, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Qin Haiyang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Haiyang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Haiyang\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"World record-holder Peaty is trying to match swimming great Michael Phelps and win a third-straight gold medal in the same event in a clash with Qin that is laced with intrigue.\", \"from\": 3064, \"to\": 3241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3124, \"end\": 3138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6885291764806856e-62, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}, {\"begin\": 3209, \"end\": 3212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\", \"score\": 0.9850633678641533, \"rank\": 0.015036014314466164, \"text\": \"Qin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Qin, the 200m world record holder, was among the 23 Chinese swimmers who tested positive for a banned drug in late 2020 to early 2021.\", \"from\": 3243, \"to\": 3377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3243, \"end\": 3246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\", \"score\": 0.9850633678641533, \"rank\": 0.015036014314466164, \"text\": \"Qin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\"}, {\"begin\": 3295, \"end\": 3302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.99994706877925, \"rank\": 4.0929666888597934e-05, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chinese swimming chiefs have denied wrongdoing, saying the swimmers tested positive after inadvertently consuming tainted food during domestic competition.\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3379, \"end\": 3386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.99994706877925, \"rank\": 4.0929666888597934e-05, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France's great swimming hope Leon Marchand will chase glory in the men's 400m individual medley, while the women's 100m butterfly title is also on the line.\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3536, \"end\": 3542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.7783821371324114, \"rank\": 0.28470942422091805, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3570, \"end\": 3578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9999999976093932, \"rank\": 1.898566724168165e-09, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Japanese 14-year-old Coco Yoshizawa won women's street skateboard gold in an all-teenage final, seeing off the challenge of compatriot Liz Akama.\", \"from\": 3694, \"to\": 3839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3694, \"end\": 3702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.8960611616130345, \"rank\": 0.1078222030482721, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier, beach volleyball fans booed Dutch player Steven van der Velde, a convicted rapist who was controversially selected for the Olympics despite his criminal past.\", \"from\": 3841, \"to\": 4008, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3878, \"end\": 3883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9989978656464681, \"rank\": 0.0006136845055871939, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van der Velde's teammate Matthew Immers spoke out in support of his colleague after the Dutch pair lost to Italy.\", \"from\": 4010, \"to\": 4123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4098, \"end\": 4103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9989978656464681, \"rank\": 0.0006136845055871939, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 4117, \"end\": 4122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999995508033962, \"rank\": 4.162154640209037e-07, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What is in the past is in the past, and he had his punishment,\\\" Immers said.\", \"from\": 4125, \"to\": 4202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia were early pacesetters in the medals table on four golds, ahead of South Korea, China, and Japan.\", \"from\": 4204, \"to\": 4311, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4281, \"end\": 4292,